sequenceDiagram
    autonumber
    actor Visitor
    participant LabPage as Lab Page UI
    participant LabList as LabList Component
    participant LabAPI as GET /api/blogs and GET /api/projects
    participant DB as PostgreSQL (Prisma)

    Visitor->>LabPage: Open /lab
    LabPage->>LabList: Mount list and controls
    LabList->>LabAPI: Fetch projects and articles (page=1)
    LabAPI->>DB: Query LAB_PROJECT and LAB_ARTICLE
    DB-->>LabAPI: Content rows
    LabAPI-->>LabList: Combined payload
    LabList-->>Visitor: Render cards, filters, and pagination

    Visitor->>LabList: Search and change filter/sort
    LabList->>LabAPI: Refetch with query params
    LabAPI->>DB: Filter, sort, paginate query
    DB-->>LabAPI: Result page + total count
    LabAPI-->>LabList: Updated result set
    LabList-->>Visitor: Render updated catalog
